Maxima was silently seething.  

In her jet mode then transformed. For a while, it would be best to be in her 
robot mode. She missed this type of flight anyway. 

Glaring back at them. "I won't say... not yet. Nor will you both log this 
flight at all! Is that understood?" glaring  back at them with her crimson 
optics as they soared along. 

--part1_181.1a8934a9.2be86108_boundary
